, {"text": "25", "bbox": [1084.7, 320.5, 1105.5, 343.5]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1127.1, 320.5, 1137.5, 343.5]}, {"text": "(6)", "bbox": [1177.7, 320.5, 1202.0, 343.5]}, {"text": "Foreign exchange contracts", "bbox": [106.3, 349.8, 335.4, 372.9]}, {"text": "(8)", "bbox": [506.9, 351.7, 531.2, 374.8]}, {"text": "9", "bbox": [603.4, 351.7, 613.9, 374.8]}, {"text": "1", "bbox": [693.0, 351.7, 703.4, 374.8]}, {"text": "Other Income/Expense", "bbox": [735.5, 351.7, 927.0, 374.8]}, {"text": "4", "bbox": [1005.5, 351.7, 1015.9, 374.8]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [1084.7, 351.7, 1105.5, 374.8]}, {"text": "1", "bbox": [1184.7, 351.7, 1195.1, 374.8]}, {"text": "Total", "bbox": [93.8, 381.1, 137.7, 404.1]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [456.3, 383.0, 466.7, 406.0]}, {"text": "16", "bbox": [503.4, 383.0, 524.3, 406.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [545.8, 383.0, 556.2, 406.0]}, {"text": "4", "bbox": [603.4, 383.0, 613.9, 406.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [635.4, 383.0, 645.8, 406.0]}, {"text": "7", "bbox": [693.0, 383.0, 703.4, 406.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [947.9, 383.0, 958.3, 406.0]}, {"text": "(12) $", "bbox": [988.1, 382.9, 1047.9, 406.0]}, {"text": "25", "bbox": [1084.7, 383.0, 1105.5, 406.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1127.1, 383.0, 1137.5, 406.0]}, {"text": "(5)", "bbox": [1177.7, 383.0, 1202.0, 406.0]}, {"text": "Fair value hedges", "bbox": [75.0, 429.1, 222.0, 452.2]}, {"text": "We designate certain futures contracts as fair value hedges of firm commitments to purchase livestock for slaughter. Our objective of", "bbox": [75.0, 454.1, 1187.0, 477.2]}, {"text": "these hedges is to minimize the risk of changes in fair value created by fluctuations in commodity prices associated with fixed price", "bbox": [75.0, 479.1, 1177.8, 502.2]}, {"text": "livestock firm commitments. We had the following aggregated notional values of outstanding forward contracts entered into to hedge", "bbox": [75.0, 504.1, 1190.2, 527.2]}, {"text": "forecasted commodity purchases which are accounted for as a fair value hedge (in millions):", "bbox": [75.0, 529.1, 845.1, 552.2]}, {"text": "Metric", "bbox": [738.1, 578.8, 793.7, 601.9]}, {"text": "September 29, 2012", "bbox": [826.5, 578.8, 993.7, 601.9]}, {"text": "October 1, 2011", "bbox": [1059.7, 578.8, 1194.5, 601.9]}, {"text": "Commodity:", "bbox": [93.8, 608.2, 199.1, 631.2]}, {"text": "Live Cattle", "bbox": [106.3, 637.3, 199.4, 660.4]}, {"text": "Pounds", "bbox": [732.3, 637.3, 793.6, 660.4]}, {"text": "232", "bbox": [961.8, 637.3, 993.0, 660.4]}, {"text": "318", "bbox": [1161.8, 637.3, 1193.0, 660.4]}, {"text": "Lean Hogs", "bbox": [106.3, 666.5, 197.1, 689.6]}, {"text": "Pounds", "bbox": [732.3, 666.5, 793.6, 689.6]}, {"text": "239", "bbox": [961.8, 666.5, 993.0, 689.6]}, {"text": "601", "bbox": [1161.8, 666.5, 1193.0, 689.6]}, {"text": "For these derivative instruments we designate and qualify as a fair value hedge, the gain or loss on the derivative, as well as the", "bbox": [75.0, 718.7, 1141.9, 741.8]}, {"text": "offsetting gain or loss on the hedged item attributable to the hedged risk, are recognized in earnings in the same period. We include the", "bbox": [75.0, 743.7, 1201.9, 766.8]}, {"text": "gain or loss on the hedged items (i.e., livestock purchase firm commitments) in the same line item, Cost of Sales, as the offsetting gain", "bbox": [75.0, 768.7, 1201.1, 791.8]}, {"text": "or loss on the related livestock forward position.", "bbox": [75.0, 793.7, 477.7, 816.8]}, {"text": "in millions", "bbox": [1104.0, 843.4, 1193.7, 866.4]}, {"text": "Consolidated", "bbox": [615.0, 874.6, 725.0, 897.7]}, {"text": "Statements of Income", "bbox": [543.3, 895.5, 725.0, 918.5]}, {"text": "Classification", "bbox": [610.4, 916.3, 725.0, 939.4]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [839.6, 916.3, 881.3, 939.4]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [996.6, 916.3, 1038.2, 939.4]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [1152.1, 916.3, 1193.8, 939.4]}, {"text": "Gain/(Loss) on forwards", "bbox": [93.8, 945.7, 298.6, 968.7]}, {"text": "Cost of Sales", "bbox": [615.0, 947.5, 725.0, 970.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [745.8, 947.5, 756.2, 970.6]}, {"text": "47", "bbox": [859.7, 947.5, 880.5, 970.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [902.1, 947.5, 912.5, 970.6]}, {"text": "(78) $", "bbox": [1009.0, 947.4, 1068.8, 970.6]}, {"text": "(58)", "bbox": [1165.2, 947.5, 1200.0, 970.6]}, {"text": "Gain/(Loss) on purchase contract", "bbox": [93.8, 976.9, 370.9, 1000.0]}, {"text": "Cost of Sales", "bbox": [615.0, 978.8, 725.0, 1001.9]}, {"text": "(47)", "bbox": [852.7, 978.7, 887.5, 1001.9]}, {"text": "78", "bbox": [1015.9, 978.8, 1036.8, 1001.9]}, {"text": "58", "bbox": [1172.2, 978.8, 1193.0, 1001.9]}, {"text": "Ineffectiveness related to our fair value hedges was not significant during fiscal 2012, 2011 and 2010.", "bbox": [75.0, 1031.2, 922.6, 1054.3]}, {"text": "Foreign net investment hedges", "bbox": [75.0, 1068.7, 330.2, 1091.8]}, {"text": "We utilize forward foreign exchange contracts to protect the value of our net investments in certain foreign subsidiaries. For derivative", "bbox": [75.0, 1093.7, 1202.1, 1116.8]}, {"text": "instruments that are designated and qualify as a hedge of a net investment in a foreign currency, the gain or loss is reported in OCI as", "bbox": [75.0, 1118.7, 1188.5, 1141.8]}, {"text": "part of the cumulative translation adjustment to the extent it is effective, with the related amounts due to or from counterparties", "bbox": [75.0, 1143.7, 1139.2, 1166.8]}, {"text": "included in other liabilities or other assets. We utilize the forward-rate method of assessing hedge effectiveness. Any ineffective", "bbox": [75.0, 1168.7, 1143.6, 1191.8]}, {"text": "portions of net investment hedges are recognized in the Consolidated Statements of Income during the period of change.", "bbox": [75.0, 1193.7, 1083.5, 1216.8]}, {"text": "Ineffectiveness related to our foreign net investment hedges was not significant during fiscal 2012, 2011 and 2010. At September 29,", "bbox": [75.0, 1218.7, 1186.4, 1241.8]}, {"text": "2012, and October 1, 2011, we had $27 million and $35 million, respectively, aggregate outstanding notional values related to our", "bbox": [75.0, 1243.7, 1162.4, 1266.8]}, {"text": "forward foreign currency contracts accounted for as foreign net investment hedges.", "bbox": [75.0, 1268.7, 767.5, 1291.8]}, {"text": "The following table sets forth the pretax impact of these derivative instruments on the Consolidated Statements of Income (in", "bbox": [75.0, 1312.5, 1125.2, 1335.5]}, {"text": "millions):", "bbox": [75.0, 1337.5, 156.0, 1360.5]}, {"text": "Gain/(Loss)", "bbox": [606.7, 1387.1, 706.2, 1410.2]}, {"text": "Recognized in OCI", "bbox": [545.3, 1408.0, 706.2, 1431.0]}, {"text": "on Derivatives", "bbox": [584.2, 1428.8, 706.2, 1451.9]}, {"text": "Consolidated", "bbox": [808.8, 1387.1, 918.7, 1410.2]}, {"text": "Statements of Income", "bbox": [737.1, 1408.0, 918.8, 1431.0]}, {"text": "Classification", "bbox": [804.2, 1428.8, 918.8, 1451.9]}, {"text": "Gain/(Loss)", "bbox": [1094.2, 1387.1, 1193.7, 1410.2]}, {"text": "Reclassified from", "bbox": [1046.1, 1408.0, 1193.7, 1431.0]}, {"text": "OCI to Earnings", "bbox": [1057.2, 1428.8, 1193.8, 1451.9]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [481.3, 1460.0, 522.9, 1483.1]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [573.6, 1460.0, 615.3, 1483.1]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [664.6, 1460.0, 706.2, 1483.1]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [968.8, 1460.0, 1010.4, 1483.1]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [1061.1, 1460.0, 1102.8, 1483.1]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [1152.1, 1460.0, 1193.8, 1483.1]}, {"text": "Net Investment Hedge – Derivatives", "bbox": [93.8, 1489.4, 403.3, 1512.5]}, {"text": "designated as hedging instruments:", "bbox": [93.8, 1510.3, 386.0, 1533.3]}, {"text": "Foreign exchange contracts", "bbox": [106.3, 1541.5, 335.4, 1564.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [452.1, 1543.4, 462.5, 1566.4]}, {"text": "(2) $", "bbox": [504.8, 1543.4, 554.2, 1566.4]}, {"text": "(2) $", "bbox": [596.5, 1543.3, 645.8, 1566.4]}, {"text": "(1) Other Income/Expense", "bbox": [688.1, 1543.3, 918.7,